Best breakfast sandwich's period.  Bacon , egg, and cheese or try the hot sausage, egg,and cheese.  Best hot sausages (Hot's) around.  Excellent Roast Pork, spicy fries with cheese.  And surprisingly he has an excellent cheessteak.  (not better than Dalessandro's but dam good)t  Tough to beat and I am Philly born and raised!
